{"id":27093,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":17}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"大众信箱,问答栏:","genre":"","count":"94","ytitle":"","mtitle":"白日见“鬼”","ftitle":"","authors":["秀桁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秀桁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问:请问白日见鬼，可真有此事吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答:这正是古已有之，于今为烈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问:何以见得?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答:君不见，一般新“鬼”们，在光天化日之下，粉墨登场吗?此非白日见鬼而何?"}]}